{
  "stem": "2735.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had organizations too, but I never got to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was not involved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had one friend that came once to visit us when I was in the small town, and she was wearing a uniform.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was very close with her, and when I came, but she wasn't involved anymore in it, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Maybe we were getting older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go through this, like, going [INAUDIBLE] and working.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it's so hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Really, what I wanted was to finish high school and to work in one of those nice buildings, the banks or something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But it would never, ever happen by the Poles because they weren't taking any Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I worked there, but the Jews-- but it was by the  Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, in this small town, we had very close friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we used to-- we used to talk about dreams, what we expect in life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to laugh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to-- and when I left, everybody gave me pictures, and we were crying and were-- [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] And then in this city, I made friends.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not-- I had a few friends that were close, like this girl that-- I-- I made some close friends, but the memory's not as deep as-- of the time that where I was born.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to love Passover.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I use to love all that baking and cooking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father, before, probably, I was born, was doing business with [INAUDIBLE] used to buy the porcelain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had the most gorgeous porcelain and crystal and-- and dishes and those tureens and candlestick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to be all hidden all the year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for Passover, they used to take it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a lot of it was on display.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
